name: QUEM DISSE "É MEU"?
description:
this week the indigenous mobilization "Levante pela terra" are taken place in Brasilia, in protest against PL490, which will go through a public hearing in the federal senate.
The amount collected from this piece is going to OYX, to support all projects aiming to strengthen the developmennmt of the indigenous causes// http://oyxabaten.com // by Carlos Moreira O.V. // tt-@falhitousbig ig-@moreiratattooer
